<http://id.gsk.com/dataset/cdisc/ct/v48/cdash/C128689-C41219> a skos:Concept ;
    ns1:identifier "C41219" ;
    skos:definition "Denotes a person having origins in any of the original peoples of Hawaii, Guam, Samoa, or other Pacific Islands. The term covers particularly people who identify themselves as part-Hawaiian, Native Hawaiian, Guamanian or Chamorro, Carolinian, Samoan, Chuu. (FDA)" ;
    skos:notation "NATIVE HAWAIIAN OR OTHER PACIFIC ISLANDER" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Native Hawaiian or Other Pacific Islander" .

